high_descs: go around the island to the left and stop at the sink on your right
open the cabinet under the sink and take out a dirty pot
take the pot to the sink
take the water filled pot out of the sink; take it to the shelf at the end of the counter behind you
place the pot on the middle shelf
anns.task_desc: place a pot with water on a shelf

high_descs: Walk towards the fridge, then hang a left and walk over to the sink.
Open the cabinet doors below the sink and take out the dirty metal pot, then close the doors.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Put the dirty metal pot in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple second turn the water off and remove the now clean pot of water.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn right to face the wooden shelving unit to the left of the counter.
Put the clean metal pot of water on the right side of the middle shelf of the wooden shelving unit.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean metal pot of water on a shelf.

high_descs: Move straight to the fridge, turn left, move to the sink, turn right to face the sink.
Open the cabinet under the sink, pick up the dirty pot in the cabinet under the sink.
Bring the dirty pot to the sink.
Wash the dirty pot in the sink with water, fill the pot with water.
Turn around with the filled pot, bring the pot to the wooden rack on the right.
Put the filled put on the middle wooden shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned pot full of water on the middle wooden rack.
